videos.description: Citadel's Kaiden Rice drives the lane and gets his shot to fall while being fouled in the first half against Clemson.
videos.headline: Citadel's Rice makes improbable and-1 between Clemson defenders

videos.description: Marcquise Reed picks the ball away from Citadel and throws it down with authority at the other end.
videos.headline: Reed steals and slams for Clemson

videos.description: Clyde Simms sends a long pass up to Aamir Simms in the paint who finishes with a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Trapp feeds Simms for powerful Clemson slam

videos.description: Shelton Mitchell doesn't make eye contact with Elijah Thomas who is waiting in the paint but fires a nice dish for a Thomas slam.
videos.headline: Mitchell executes perfect no-look for Thomas jam
